WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.700 --> 00:00:02.001
- Garfield!
- [yelps]

00:00:02.034 --> 00:00:03.903
- A supernatural presence
is close at hand.

00:00:03.936 --> 00:00:06.339
I can feel it.
Set the bait, boys,

00:00:06.372 --> 00:00:07.807
set the bait.

00:00:07.840 --> 00:00:09.709
Here is paté for the ghost-dog,

00:00:09.742 --> 00:00:12.578 align:end position:100%
here is a wire hanger
for the ghost-baby.

00:00:12.611 --> 00:00:15.381 align:end position:100%
Trio of home-baked macarons
for...

00:00:15.414 --> 00:00:17.016
[together]
Sticky Jonathan.

00:00:17.049 --> 00:00:20.953
- But Mr. Peepers,
that's my best friend.

00:00:20.986 --> 00:00:22.555 align:start size:75% position:25%
- Other people will die.

00:00:22.588 --> 00:00:25.658 align:end position:100%
You'll make friends
with their ghosts.

00:00:25.691 --> 00:00:27.160 align:start position:0%
- Mr. Peepers,

00:00:27.193 --> 00:00:29.328
how do you know so much
about ghosts?

00:00:29.361 --> 00:00:32.331
<i> [mystical woodwind music]</i>

00:00:32.364 --> 00:00:33.699 align:start size:41% position:59%
- Garfield...

00:00:33.732 --> 00:00:37.070
<i> ♪ ♪</i>

00:00:37.103 --> 00:00:40.239 align:end position:100%
I've never told anybody
this story before,

00:00:40.272 --> 00:00:45.445 align:end position:100%
but my
great-great-great-grandpappy...

00:00:45.478 --> 00:00:47.480
was a ghost.
- [yelps]

00:00:47.513 --> 00:00:50.383 align:end position:100%
- Yes, Garfield,
I have ghost blood

00:00:50.416 --> 00:00:54.887 align:end position:100%
coursing through me.
It is my family's eternal shame.

00:00:54.920 --> 00:00:57.457 align:start position:0%
- Is that why they call
you Spiritwalker?

00:00:57.490 --> 00:00:58.791
- What?
Oh, no, no.

00:00:58.824 --> 00:01:00.493
Don't be ridiculous.
They call me Spiritwalker

00:01:00.526 --> 00:01:02.261
because I walk
with such great enthusiasm.

00:01:02.294 --> 00:01:03.563
Observe.

00:01:03.596 --> 00:01:05.598
<i> [glamorous music]</i>

00:01:05.631 --> 00:01:07.300 align:start position:0%
- Oh!

00:01:07.333 --> 00:01:09.202 align:start position:0%
Oh, Mr. Peepers!

00:01:09.235 --> 00:01:13.272 align:start position:0%
Mister--oh!
Look out!

00:01:13.305 --> 00:01:16.442
Mr. Peepers, look at you go!

00:01:16.475 --> 00:01:19.008
[laughing delightedly]
Oh, my goodness.

